39:36.333 --> 39:39.571
♪ swayin' in the summer breeze ♪

39:39.810 --> 39:43.168
♪ showin' off their silver leaves ♪

39:43.301 --> 39:45.874
♪ as we walked by ♪

39:45.969 --> 39:47.732
♪ soft ♪

39:47.830 --> 39:50.700
♪ kisses on a summer's day ♪

39:51.217 --> 39:54.546
♪ laughin' all our cares away ♪

39:54.866 --> 39:57.482
